name: Borscht
instruction: Borscht, also known as beetroot soup or Suber soup, is a thick vegetable soup originated in Ukraine.

name: Chicken Salad
instruction: Chicken salad is any salad with chicken as the main ingredient. Other common ingredients may include mayonnaise, boiled eggs, celery, onions, peppers, pickles and various mustards.

name: Waffles
instruction: A waffle is a dish made from leavened batter or dough that is cooked between two plates that are patterned to give a characteristic size, shape, and surface impression.

name: Osso Buco
instruction: Ossobuco or osso buco is a specialty of Lombard cuisine of cross-cut veal shanks braised with vegetables, white wine and broth.
